TO DOWNLOAD parodus2ccsp component SOURCE:
https://github.com/Comcast/parodus2ccsp

STEPS TO BUILD parodus2ccsp component for YOCTO

1 Create a folder named "parodus2ccsp" under "meta-rdk/recipes-support/" path
2 Copy the parodus2ccsp_1.0.bb file to the "meta-rdk/recipes-support/parodus2ccsp"
3 Create another directory named parodus2ccsp under "meta-rdk/recipes-support/parodus2ccsp"
4 Place the parodus2ccsp_cmake.patch file under "meta-rdk/recipes-support/parodus2ccsp/parodus2ccsp"

To include parodus2ccsp as part of the Image 
Add parodus2ccsp under RDEPENDS_packagegroup-rdk-oss-broadband in meta-rdk/recipes-core/packagegroups/packagegroup-rdk-ccsp-broadband.bb

To Build the component

bitbake parodus2ccsp


